    rdfs:comment "Anomaly pattern indicating high CPU usage coupled with low network throughput, often a sign of a bottleneck or misconfiguration."@en .

<anomalypattern/InterfaceFlap>
    a noria:AnomalyPattern, folio:FailureMode ;
    rdfs:label "Network Interface Flap Anomaly"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Anomaly pattern for frequent up/down transitions of a network interface, suggesting physical layer issues or faulty hardware."@en .

